{{Infobox dungeon |name = Team Rockets Hideout |image = [[File:Team Rockets Hideout.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Team Rockets Hideout |tokens = 5,500 |location = Mahogany Town }} '''Team Rockets Hideout''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Johto]]. It initially has 36 tiles arranged in a 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 15 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
